=edit#_Toc424923269\">1.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Approach&nbsp; 5</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923270\">1.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Document Organisation&nbsp; 5</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923271\">2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Summary of Findings&nbsp;&nbsp; 6</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923272\">2.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Departmental Business Processes and Documents&nbsp; 6</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923273\">2.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Business Impact Assessment 13</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923274\">2.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Critical Business Records &amp; Documents for each Department 14</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923275\">2.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Regulatory &amp; Statutory Reporting Requirements&nbsp; 15</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923276\">2.5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Summary of Key Observations&nbsp; 15</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923277\">2.6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Conclusion&nbsp; 15</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923278\">2.7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BIA Questions&nbsp; 16</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923279\">SECTION 2: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;BUSINESS CONTINUITY PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp; 17</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admi