nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Disaster declaration&nbsp; 20</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923292\">1.9.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Disaster Notification&nbsp; 20</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923293\">1.9.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; External communications&nbsp; 20</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923294\">1.10&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum Business Continuity standards&nbsp; 20</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923295\">1.10.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Data backup policy&nbsp; 20</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923296\">1.10.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Backup media storage policy: 21</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923297\">1.10.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Offsite backup facilities&nbsp; 21</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923298\">1.10.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Storage of Hard copy files and Documents&nbsp; 22</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923299\">1.10.5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cash Management 22</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923300\">1.10.6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stationery Management 22</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://documents.musoni.co.ke/wp-admin/post.php?post=19&amp;action=edit#_Toc424923301\">1.10.7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&