&nbsp;&nbsp; OK- Undamaged</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DBU - Damaged, but usable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DS - Damaged, requires salvage before use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D- Destroyed, requires reconstruction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a name=\"_Toc424923355\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359900465\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359899464\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359832267\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359722723\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359397036\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359395518\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359395133\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359388079\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359387315\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359221396\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359214737\"></a><a name=\"_Toc359214356\"></a><a name=\"_Toc358182148\"></a><a name=\"_Toc358180956\"></a><a name=\"_Toc358180504\"></a><a name=\"_Toc358074557\"></a><a name=\"_Toc357997265\"></a><a name=\"_Toc357995652\"></a><a name=\"_Toc357995146\"></a>1.13&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Appendix H: Building Evacuation Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In preparation for any emergency, which may involve the evacuation of a building, all staff will leave the incident site with some useful information for their desk or job if possible. This will be a list of items like flash disks, laptops, tablets to say the least which each member of staff should endeavor to collect from their surrounding work area.&nbsp;<strong>It must be&nbsp;</strong><strong>emphasised</strong><strong>&nbsp;that the items should be small and few in number, so as not to delay evacuation or risk personal safety.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Business Continuity Plan was approved by the Board of Directors of Musoni Kenya Ltd (MKL) on 29th&nbsp;January 2016 and took immediate effect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Signed by:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>___________________________________&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs